# Phase-4 FP loop & runbooks runtime data.
#
# This directory is the default location for:
#   - feedback.sqlite           : analyst feedback + suppression rules (TR1NITY_API_FP_DB)
#   - fp_classifier.pkl         : Layer-2 sklearn model produced by `make retrain`
#   - fp_classifier_report.json : training report companion
#
# The actual data files are gitignored (see top-level .gitignore).
